lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人最鐘意開頭呢幾句<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8sx0FEP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8sx0FEP.png&h=ef398871&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1216063a640361b889f8df551cfc0618da03f70","tid":1249174,"uid":148236,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T17:56:12.000Z","msg":"其實呢幾句都好正，好難揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sNJ7kGz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsNJ7kGz.png&h=8c27aa5c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44b781f331f605b181b567155529bc35eec1a46a","tid":1249174,"uid":164382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:00:41.000Z","msg":"聽到瞓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nG持"},{"pid":"9c0d46f32c2d62d25c6a65d699b2f9c01ef94054","tid":1249174,"uid":148236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"44b781f331f605b181b567155529bc35eec1a46a","tid":1249174,"uid":164382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:00:41.000Z","msg":"聽到瞓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nG持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:14:52.000Z","msg":"係呢，我都係loop咗好幾次，覺得要分享畀更多嘅人聽到，先上黎開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecde020451c662a108c0d6000a3be3335920bd31","tid":1249174,"uid":148236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"44b781f331f605b181b567155529bc35eec1a46a","tid":1249174,"uid":164382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:00:41.000Z","msg":"聽到瞓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nG持"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T18:19:02.000Z","msg":"共勉之啊絲打<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o4t3DAX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo4t3DAX.png&h=7b15cfdb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f